		<title>Moonshot by TechCabal unveils 2026 theme, &#8220;Courage &#038; Conviction — Building for a New World&#8221;</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/29/moonshot-by-techcabal-unveils-2026-theme/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Editor]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 13:27:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Moonshot]]></category>
