		<title>Kenya leads Bloomberg’s list of African startups to watch </title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/29/kenya-leads-bloombergs-2026-africa-startups-to-watch-list/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Kenn Abuya]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 12:17:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Startups]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Bloomberg News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Bloomberg News' 2026 Africa Startups to Watch]]></category>
