<p>The biggest reason to pick this phone is software support. Samsung confirmed the Galaxy A07 will receive six major Android OS upgrades and six years of security updates. That is far more than the one or two updates you get from Tecno, Infinix, or Xiaomi at this price. If you keep phones for three to five years, this matters a lot.</p>



