</ul>



<p>The Redmi 15C has a 6.9-inch 120Hz HD+ display, a Helio G81 Ultra-class chip, 4GB RAM, 128GB storage, dual-SIM 4G, and Android 15 with HyperOS.</p>



<p>This is the newest Xiaomi C-series phone available in Nigeria. It ships with Android 15 and benefits from Xiaomi’s longer software support window compared to Tecno and Infinix phones at the same price.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>10. Tecno Spark 40 (4GB + 4GB Virtual / 128GB)</strong></h4>



